title: Microsoft Virtual PC 2007 SP1
description:
MS Virtual PC 2007 SP1

Hyper-V offer better experience. But if your machines don't support Hyper-V features may be this tool still usefull.

Windows 8:

- rename "setup.exe" with other name before execute.
- after finish installation, go to %system drive%Program FilesMicrosoft Virtual PC
- rename "Virtual PC.exe" with other name before execute.

If have any problems, please ask the maker of this software, not me.

THX.
